      <title>美国发布癌症警告 导致亚洲酒精饮料股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/alcoholic-beverage-stocks-slide-in-asia-on-us-cancer-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国卫生局局长指出饮酒与癌症风险增加之间的直接联系并要求贴上警告标签之后，亚洲酒类和啤酒制造商的股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/alcoholic-beverage-stocks-slide-in-asia-on-us-cancer-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 03:08:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
